Description:
    You can modify shopping cart views

Example:
    rails generate shopping_cart:views

    This will create:
        app/views/shopping_cart/carts/show.html.slim

        app/views/shopping_cart/checkout/address.html.slim
        app/views/shopping_cart/checkout/completed.html.slim
        app/views/shopping_cart/checkout/confirm.html.slim
        app/views/shopping_cart/checkout/delivery.html.slim
        app/views/shopping_cart/checkout/payment.html.slim

        app/views/shopping_cart/orders/index.html.slim
        app/views/shopping_cart/orders/show.html.slim
